# AISplinter License

AISplinter is an open-source project with a dual-license model:

### 1. SDKs, UI Components, and Utilities
All files under the `packages/` directory are licensed under the **MIT License**. This allows developers to freely embed AISplinter tools into their own applications (commercial or otherwise) without restriction.

### 2. Server, Adapters, and Core Infrastructure
All files under the `apps/server/` and `adapters/` directories are licensed under the **GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 (AGPL-3.0)**. This ensures that the core middleware remains open and that improvements made by those hosting the service are shared back with the community.

